No, you can do it.

728
00:29:12,792 --> 00:29:14,710
- I don't get it.
- You can do it, Hye-ri.

729
00:29:14,711 --> 00:29:16,295
- You can do it.
- I'm too nervous.

730
00:29:16,296 --> 00:29:17,629
You can do it!

731
00:29:17,630 --> 00:29:19,173
