732
00:29:19,174 --> 00:29:20,799
- I'm so nervous.
- Don't be.

733
00:29:20,800 --> 00:29:22,593
- I'm too stressed.
- You're okay.

734
00:29:22,594 --> 00:29:24,470
- I'm so anxious.
- Hye-ri.

735
00:29:24,471 --> 00:29:25,429
Come on, Hye-ri.

736
00:29:25,430 --> 00:29:26,889
