if it doesn't work.

799
00:31:38,396 --> 00:31:39,855
- Geez.
- We have three.

800
00:31:39,856 --> 00:31:40,772
THREATENING

801
00:31:40,773 --> 00:31:43,568
WITH THE SMOKE GRENADES
ROUND 56

802
00:31:44,193 --> 00:31:45,944
