- Focus.

803
00:31:45,945 --> 00:31:47,113
Let's do this.

804
00:31:55,788 --> 00:31:57,164
This is insane.

805
00:31:57,165 --> 00:31:59,791
But I think we have the hang of it.

806
00:31:59,792 --> 00:32:02,127
AFTER GETTING THE HANG OF IT
57TH FAIL

807
00:32:02,128 --> 00:32:03,128
It's okay.

808
00:32:03,129 --> 00:32:04,379
61ST FAIL

809
00:32:04,380 --> 00:32:05,923
It's okay.

810
00:32:05,924 --> 00:32:07,382
63RD FAIL

811
00:32:07,383 --> 00:32:08,467
- I'm sorry.
- It's okay.

812
00:32:08,468 --> 00:32:10,010
- It's okay.
- It's fine.

813
00:32:10,011 --> 00:32:10,970
It's really okay.

814
00:32:13,056 --> 00:32:14,139
Come on, Hye-ri!

815
00:32:14,140 --> 00:32:16,141
- It's okay, Hye-ri.
- It's okay.

816
00:32:16,142 --> 00:32:17,976
SECOND WAVE OF DESPAIR

817
00:32:17,977 --> 00:32:19,853
- It's okay.
- It's hard.

818
00:32:19,854 --> 00:32:21,605
Whenever someone messes up,

819
00:32:21,606 --> 00:32:24,775
- "it's okay" is now our first response.
- That's right.

820
00:32:24,776 --> 00:32:25,818
- Don't lose hope.
- Okay.

821
00:32:27,028 --> 00:32:29,821
The viewers have no idea
how long we've done this for.

822
00:32:29,822 --> 00:32:31,531
So, they won't get why we're tired.

823
00:32:31,532 --> 00:32:33,659
- It's unacceptable, so let's keep going.
- You're right.

824
00:32:33,660 --> 00:32:35,577
KEEPING THEIR ENERGY UP
ROUND 67

825
00:32:35,578 --> 00:32:37,245
SEAMLESSLY
ROUND 68

826
00:32:37,246 --> 00:32:39,247
DON'T MAKE IT OBVIOUS
ROUND 69

827
00:32:39,248 --> 00:32:40,959
GROWING SILENT
ROUND 70

828
