925
00:37:59,527 --> 00:38:02,529
IF YOU LIFT THE KEY CARD

926
00:38:02,530 --> 00:38:03,864
It must be the shadows.

927
00:38:04,657 --> 00:38:07,827
I think it matches this small pattern.

928
00:38:08,577 --> 00:38:10,996
They look really similar.

929
00:38:10,997 --> 00:38:11,998
SIMILAR PATTERN IDENTIFIED

930
00:38:12,581 --> 00:38:15,626
ON HIGH-ALERT

931
00:38:18,421 --> 00:38:19,587
It's okay. Stay focused.

932
00:38:19,588 --> 00:38:22,008
It's okay. We'll keep a lookout.

933
00:38:23,551 --> 00:38:25,427
So, we just focus on this pattern…

934
00:38:25,428 --> 00:38:27,430
-…and ignore the rest, right?
- Yes, the small pattern.

935
00:38:27,930 --> 00:38:30,683
But it's not fitting right.

936
00:38:32,893 --> 00:38:35,520
It might be faster to combine them

937
00:38:35,521 --> 00:38:37,356
and look for numbers.

938
00:38:37,857 --> 00:38:39,899
It's just strange that the similar pattern

939
00:38:39,900 --> 00:38:42,610
- is in the same spot.
- That's true.

940
00:38:42,611 --> 00:38:43,945
Maybe it's this way round

941
00:38:43,946 --> 00:38:45,488
- so it doesn't overlap.
- I think so.

942
00:38:45,489 --> 00:38:46,573
- That seems right.
- Right?

943
00:38:46,574 --> 00:38:48,408
- If we put it here…
- Is that a three?

944
00:38:48,409 --> 00:38:50,036
- It looks like a three.
- It's a three.

945
00:38:50,619 --> 00:38:51,995
- Three…
- Three…

946
00:38:51,996 --> 00:38:54,581
- Three and eight.
- Is this an eight?

947
00:38:54,582 --> 00:38:55,957
But there's no line here.

948
00:38:55,958 --> 00:38:57,208
It's six.

949
00:38:57,209 --> 00:38:58,793
- It connects like this.
- It's four.

950
00:38:58,794 --> 00:38:59,794
- It's four, right?
- It is.

951
00:38:59,795 --> 00:39:01,296
It's 3648.

952
00:39:01,297 --> 00:39:02,465
- Then 3648.
- Let's try 3648.

953
00:39:10,806 --> 00:39:12,725
- Go on in.
- They're good.

954
00:39:13,434 --> 00:39:14,726
You just combined them, right?

955
00:39:14,727 --> 00:39:16,354
- Yes.
- Great job.

956
00:39:16,937 --> 00:39:18,481
I'm so sick of colors.

957
00:39:19,273 --> 00:39:20,649
What are they for this time?

958
00:39:21,150 --> 00:39:22,776
A LARGE PLATFORM

959
00:39:22,777 --> 00:39:25,487
What's with the colored squares?
It's making me nervous.

960
00:39:25,488 --> 00:39:27,447
I was very unhappy.

961
00:39:27,448 --> 00:39:29,657
I wonder what it is.

962
00:39:29,658 --> 00:39:31,701
Do we stand on it?

963
00:39:31,702 --> 00:39:33,119
SAFETY CHECK

964
00:39:33,120 --> 00:39:34,162
We can't. It's glass.

965
00:39:34,163 --> 00:39:36,664
- I don't think it's safe.
- No, it's made of glass.

966
00:39:36,665 --> 00:39:39,042
Should we each pick a color?

967
00:39:39,043 --> 00:39:41,920
- Should we stick to our earlier colors?
- There must be something.

968
00:39:41,921 --> 00:39:43,588
- Should we put our hands on them?
- Okay.

969
00:39:43,589 --> 00:39:44,799
PUTTING HANDS ON EACH COLOR

970
00:39:45,383 --> 00:39:46,299
Is anything happening?

971
00:39:46,300 --> 00:39:47,718
What is this?

972
